WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.509
Find a spot where the light is on your face, not behind you.

00:00:03.559 --> 00:00:07.069
Standing in front of a bay door at noon turns you into a

00:00:07.119 --> 00:00:10.628
silhouette. Use shop lighting deliberately. The customer needs to see your expression —

00:00:10.678 --> 00:00:13.366
that is most of what makes the video feel personal.
